Program: Outlook
Title: Back from the dead three times
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0104j63
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 8 Nov 2012
Dan Eley, the British man who was paralysed from the neck down after diving into a lagoon in the Colombian jungle describes coming back from the dead three times. We also meet the tortoise expert from Senegal who looks after 6,000 of them. Plus we're joined live by the Kadavu Choir from Fiji. Image: Dan Eley Show less